FBIS4-2872 "drchi072_a_94001" FBIS-CHI-94-072 Daily Report 14 Apr 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS General Foreign Ministry Spokesman Holds News Briefing Foreign Ministry Spokesman Holds News Briefing Announces NPC Delegation Visit OW1404083494 Beijing XINHUA in English 0808 GMT 14 Apr 94 OW1404083494 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, April 14 (XINHUA) -- A delegation from China's National People's Congress (NPC) is to visit New Zealand, Western Samoa, Papua New Guinea and Australia later this month, a Chinese Foreign Ministry spokesman announced here this afternoon. According to the spokesman, the delegation, which will be headed by Vice-Chairman Tian Jiyun of the NPC Standing Committee, will pay official good-will visits to the above mentioned four countries from April 18 at the invitation of their parliaments.
